OL,3,CKeir Starmer vows to round off local
OL,4,Celection campaign 'fighting for every
OL,5,Cvote'
OL,7,FSir Keir Starmer has vowed to go into
OL,8,Fpolling day "fighting for every vote"
OL,9,Fbut acknowledged Labour could be in
OL,10,Ffor a "challenge", as political
OL,11,Fleaders conclude their local election
OL,12,Fcampaign trails.
OL,14,FWednesday marks the final full day of
OL,15,Fcampaigning before polls open on
OL,16,FThursday across England, Scotland and
OL,17,FWales.
OL,19,FAlmost 25,000 candidates are fighting
OL,20,Fto be elected to more than 5,000 seats
OL,21,Fon 136 councils across England.
OL,26,@pD@MOUpD@eO]rD@GOUrD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
