OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778051113
OL,3,CKeir Starmer vows to round off local
OL,4,Celection campaign 'fighting for every
OL,5,Cvote'
OL,7,FIn Scotland, all 129 seats are up for
OL,8,Felection in Holyrood, while voters in
OL,9,FWales will choose a set of 96 members
OL,10,Fof the Senedd.
OL,12,FAt a Labour campaign rally in south
OL,13,FLondon on Tuesday, Prime Minister Sir
OL,14,FKeir was asked how he could convince
OL,15,Fvoters to support his party in
OL,16,FThursday's election, as it faces a
OL,17,Fslump in opinion polls.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778051113
OL,3,CKeir Starmer vows to round off local
OL,4,Celection campaign 'fighting for every
OL,5,Cvote'
OL,7,F"As you can see, we've got a fantastic
OL,8,FLabour team working every single day
OL,9,Fin London and across the country,
OL,10,Fcampaigning with fantastic councillors
OL,11,Fand candidates and with a very
OL,12,Fpositive message," he replied.
OL,14,F"Of course, it's going to be a
OL,15,Fchallenge, but it is really important
OL,16,Fwe go in fighting for every vote,
OL,17,Fwhich has to be earned, in relation to
OL,18,Fthis."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@RO]vD@AOUzD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30404
