OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778051113
OL,3,CKeir Starmer vows to round off local
OL,4,Celection campaign 'fighting for every
OL,5,Cvote'
OL,7,FIn a further pitch to voters, Sir Keir
OL,8,Fwrote in Wednesday's Mirror newspaper:
OL,9,F"On Thursday, when you go to put your
OL,10,Fvote in the ballot box, there's a
OL,11,Fclear choice on that piece of paper.
OL,13,F"Unity or division. Progress versus
OL,14,Fthe politics of anger. The right plan
OL,15,Ffor our country up against easy
OL,16,Fanswers that will lead us nowhere."
OL,26,@qD@AOUuD@AOUxD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
