OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778051113
OL,3,CKeir Starmer vows to round off local
OL,4,Celection campaign 'fighting for every
OL,5,Cvote'
OL,7,FThe Welsh Labour leader has faced
OL,8,Fquestions about whether Thursday's
OL,9,Fvote could see her party lose control
OL,10,Fof the Senedd, with Plaid Cymru or
OL,11,FReform UK taking control.
OL,13,F"I'm certainly hoping that they won't
OL,14,Fdo that," Baroness Eluned Morgan of
OL,15,FEly told The Telegraph.
OL,17,F"But there is a danger that that could
OL,18,Fhappen, and I don't want to see that
OL,19,Fhappening.
OL,26,@uD@AOUvD@IO]yD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778051113
OL,3,CKeir Starmer vows to round off local
OL,4,Celection campaign 'fighting for every
OL,5,Cvote'
OL,7,F"I do hope people will reflect on what
OL,8,Fthis election is really about ` and it
OL,9,Fisn't a time, I think, to pick a fight
OL,10,Fwith Starmer. There's a general
OL,11,Felection, that's the time to do that."
OL,13,FIn Solihull, West Midlands, Kemi
OL,14,FBadenoch told Conservative Party
OL,15,Fcampaigners on Tuesday that Sir Keir
OL,16,Fwas already fighting a "shadow
OL,17,Fleadership contest", with Labour
OL,18,Fbackers "talking about what their
OL,19,Fparty should stand for two years into
OL,20,FGovernment".
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@fO]xD@XOUyD@SO]zD@IOU|D@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
