CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778051113
OL,3,CKeir Starmer vows to round off local
OL,4,Celection campaign 'fighting for every
OL,5,Cvote'
OL,7,FShe also said: "The Conservative Party
OL,8,Fis on the side of people who want to
OL,9,Fget on, people who are saving up to
OL,10,Fbuy a home, mums and dads who are
OL,11,Ftrying to build a better life for
OL,12,Ftheir children.
OL,14,F"These are our people and we are
OL,15,Ffighting for them at this election `
OL,16,Fhere in Solihull, all over Scotland
OL,17,Fand Wales, in London, in Essex, in
OL,18,FSwindon, in Sunderland, in Norfolk, in
OL,19,FPlymouth, everywhere the people have a
OL,20,Fvote."
OL,26,@oD@POUvD@AOU|D@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
