OL,3,CKeir Starmer vows to round off local
OL,4,Celection campaign 'fighting for every
OL,5,Cvote'
OL,7,FIn a video message to his party's
OL,8,Fbackers, filmed in the South Wales
OL,9,FSenedd seat of Caerdydd Penarth and
OL,10,Fposted to X, Mr Polanski said: "This
OL,11,Fis a vital moment that will change
OL,12,FWales forever."
OL,14,FPlaid Cymru leader Rhun ap Iorwerth
OL,15,Ftold his supporters the Welsh election
OL,16,Fwas "going down to the wire".
OL,18,FAlso in a video message posted to X,
OL,19,FMr ap Iorwerth said: "The future of
OL,20,FWales depends on this."
OL,26,@rD@`OUtD@OO]xD@EOUxD@\O]{D@VOU|D@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
