OL,3,CKeir Starmer vows to round off local
OL,4,Celection campaign 'fighting for every
OL,5,Cvote'
OL,7,FHe described Plaid as "the only party
OL,8,Frooted in Wales, with a plan for
OL,9,FWales, focused only on Wales,
OL,10,Faccountable only to the people of
OL,11,FWales, and the only party that can
OL,12,Fbeat Reform".
OL,26,@oD@WOUtD@LO]
